{"tid":2205278,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[漫畫考察恩物] Big Comic Spirit創刊40週年特設「非日常な彼女展」","createTime":"2020-09-16T16:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T16:42:57.000Z","uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e60b599531125e3ccb8604ff5b69bb9569783575","tid":2205278,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:42:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bigcomicbros.net/spirits40/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbigcomicbros.net%2Fspirits40%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BobsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=dbef699a\" target=\"_blank\">https://bigcomicbros.net/spirits40/</a><br />\n「非日常な彼女」本來係連載緊既月刊長壽企劃，主題係「女性を自由に描く」。<br />\n<br />\n40週年搞咗個網站將2010年以來既作品公開展覽，附帶當時既訪談同作品解說，依家公開到2015年，會每個星期更新。<br />\n<br />\n好多知名漫畫家都有畫過呢個企劃，其中包括淺野一二O、浦澤直樹、東村明子等，想要系統地了解10年代想像力呢個展覽應該係唔錯既材料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7G2xaWB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7G2xaWB.jpg&h=a4065013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DfQiQWC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDfQiQWC.jpg&h=c80d73a8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}